MCgrid Interface for Monte Carlo event generators to APPLgrid.
Website: http://mcgrid.hepforge.org
Support: mcgrid@projects.hepforge.org

Software Requirements:
	• Rivet version 2.0.0 or later.
	• APPLgrid version 1.4.28 or later.
	• boost::Filesystem version 3 or later, with libboost-filesystem-dev
	• Optionally pkg-config for path management.
  
The MCgrid package has been tested with the SHERPA v2.0 event generator
available at: http://sherpa.hepforge.org/trac/wiki

To install the interface:
	./configure [options]
	make
	(sudo) make install

If installing to a nonstandard directory, please ensure that the mcgrid.pc
file is in the PKG_CONFIG_PATH.

Example MCgrid-enhanced analyses may be found in the
	/examples
directory, and (in future) on the HepForge page.
